text.section:
The Kentucky Board of Pharmacy shall promulgate administrative regulations pursuant to KRS Chapter 13A to implement the provisions of this section that shall include but not be limited to:
Accuracy of the automated pharmacy system;
Security of the system;
Recordkeeping, including but not limited to electronic signatures of authorized users;
Inventory management;
Labeling or reporting requirements that include identification of the dispensing pharmacy, the prescription number, the name of the patient, and the name of the prescriber; and
Training for authorized users.
